{"tid":2409074,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"唔打針唔畀去食飯 陳肇始：接種疫苗為進入食肆等場所條件","createTime":"2021-02-15T13:13:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T04:50:36.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"82ac223c83d9ae269bd55ef1f48e13049f588b6f","tid":2409074,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TE3NqbFA9EnlrrO7vMtntkcaH24=/1200x675/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/57RU7R63MJF4XAJROGXFUBNKJQ.jfif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTE3NqbFA9EnlrrO7vMtntkcaH24%3D%2F1200x675%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F57RU7R63MJF4XAJROGXFUBNKJQ.jfif&h=d0f4b1bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢肺炎疫苗未到，港府已密謀各種催谷接種率的方法。據商業電台報道，食物及衞生局局長陳肇始表示，不排除日後把接種武肺疫苗，列為市民進入食肆等表列處所的條件之一，意味沒有接種疫苗的市民，可能不能光顧食肆或到戲院等公眾地方。衞生防護中心總監林文健則指，接種武肺疫苗應是市民自願的行為，疫苗對減低病毒傳播的成效亦需時間及數據了解。<br />\n<br />\n突提出市民入食肆前須出示打針證明<br />\n<br />\n陳肇始接受商台專訪，就年初七後逐步放寬表列處所社交限制措施時，提出數個條件，「一方面就係一定要啲員工要去做檢測；第二呢，都需要嗰個『安心出行』（程式）；咁第三，當然如果我哋話，啊，真係到到有打疫苗嘅時候，就希望大家都會打疫苗啦。」<br />\n但翻查過去陳肇始在公開場合的發言，不曾提及政府擬要市民進入食肆前要先出示打針證明，才可用膳。《蘋果》正向食衞局查詢。"},{"pid":"e572cdfca24ff5b23f923694829de72a896606e6","tid":2409074,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210215/YQR4NS7ECNC4PERAJSFCPMPYAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210215%2FYQR4NS7ECNC4PERAJSFCPMPYAU%2F&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=751abf16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210215%2FYQR4NS7ECNC4PERAJSFCPMPYAU%2F&h=ab3f46f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210215/YQR4NS7ECNC4PERAJSFCPMPYAU/</a>"},{"pid":"c7f0cd08567dc60fd42bf2f6eac47c3704a98